metadata.description: JAMES PATTERSON'S SMASH HIT SERIES RETURNS FOR A TRIUMPHANT CONCLUSION! THE FLOCK is tired of running. They're ready to take the fight directly to JEB and the ERASERS! But things get complicated when the line between friend and enemy is blurred. And all the while, MAXIMUM RIDE keeps hearing that voice in her head – the voice that says she's destined to save the world!
metadata.name: Max Ride: Final Flight
